<Algorithm code="           1. Assert: If _module_ is a Cyclic Module Record, then _module_.[[Status]] is not ~new~ or ~unlinked~.           1. Let _namespace_ be _module_.[[Namespace]].           1. If _namespace_ is ~empty~, then             1. Let _exportedNames_ be _module_.GetExportedNames().             1. Let _unambiguousNames_ be a new empty List.             1. For each element _name_ of _exportedNames_, do               1. Let _resolution_ be _module_.ResolveExport(_name_).               1. If _resolution_ is a ResolvedBinding Record, append _name_ to _unambiguousNames_.             1. Set _namespace_ to ModuleNamespaceCreate(_module_, _unambiguousNames_).           1. Return _namespace_.         ">
